in such ways.

656
01:24:25,080 --> 01:24:27,833
So, I don't have the guts, huh?.

657
01:25:07,800 --> 01:25:10,872
I was for you, Norman.
Believed in you.

658
01:25:11,680 --> 01:25:14,672
You made a fool of me.
Look what you did to yourself!

659
01:25:15,080 --> 01:25:16,672
Why, Norman, why?.

660
01:25:17,080 --> 01:25:20,834
Good God, son,
you'll never get out again.

661
01:25:23,200 --> 01:25:24,792
They're going to lock you up forever.

662
01:25:26,280 --> 01:25:30,432
But I'll be free.
I'll finally be free.

